		{
			dependencies: ["330FEE9467B9D8A6"]
			description: ["Botania's mystical flowers bloom across every biome, each with a distinct color and function. Gathering four unique types and reading the Lexica Botania is your introduction to a mana-based magic system that runs in parallel with your soul cultivation. Botania and Soul Land share material gates — you will need both."]
