		{
			dependencies: ["5FC6C2D842B38AD2"]
			description: ["The soul ring is now bound to your martial soul. Your spirit beast hunting should continue — Yellow Rings (100-year beasts) await in the Outer Forest, and Purple Rings (1000-year) in the Inner Forest. Each ring slot unlocks at a specific cultivation rank, so prioritize rank advancement alongside ring collection."]
