		{
			dependencies: ["39E3B53123CFECC7"]
			description: ["Mana is Botania's energy currency. Generating flowers produce it; Mana Spreaders beam it into Mana Pools. The Mana Pool stores it for use in crafting and mana infusion. Keep your pool topped up — Manasteel production alone requires thousands of mana per ingot, and the Terra Plate demands an uninterrupted sustained supply."]
