			]
			description: ["Manasteel is produced by infusing Iron Ingots with 3,000 mana in Botania's mana infusion process — drop the ingot into a Mana Pool. In this pack, the infusion recipe has been modified to also yield Spirit Steel Ingots, gating mid-tier Soul Land crafting behind your Botania progress. This is the first major convergence of the two systems."]
