		{
			dependencies: ["792CE5342E2F27E8"]
			description: ["The Yellow Ring is absorbed from a 100-year spirit beast — far older than the creatures found at the Star Dou Forest Edge. You must venture into the Outer Forest, where soul power density rises and the predators grow proportionally more dangerous. Each ring permanently adds an active skill to your martial soul; choose the beast that complements your fighting style. The Spirit Detector reveals the age of nearby beasts — use it to find a 100-year target before committing to the hunt."]
