		{
			dependencies: ["5815ABC064A26E99"]
			description: ["Spirit Elder marks your recognition as a second-tier cultivator — ranks 11 through 20. Your Yellow Ring slot is now active, and your soul power has stabilized enough to begin absorbing century-aged beast skills. Maintain steady breakthrough cycles and manage your Foundation Stability carefully. Overuse of herbs generates instability; meditation and pills are the remedy. The gap between an undisciplined scholar and a disciplined elder widens fast at this stage."]
