		}
		{
			dependencies: ["792CE5342E2F27E8"]
			description: ["Press [B] to attempt a Breakthrough when your soul power reaches the next rank threshold. Press [Shift+B] to consume a Foundation Pill and boost success rate. Foundation Stability is a hidden stat: herb overuse, death, and failed breakthroughs each add instability points, which lower success probability and slow meditation speed. Stability recovers through meditation and resets faster with pills. Stock Breakthrough Pills before every major threshold — they drop from dungeon chests and high-tier beast kills."]
			id: "7DAE3A2B358785F6"
