		{
			dependencies: ["4BCFBD1E3F78FB52"]
			description: ["At rank 30, your Martial Soul Transformation first manifests. Press [V] to activate T1 — the physical traits of your martial soul overlay your form: limb augmentations, elemental traces, and a temporary amplification of attack power and sensory range. Two further tiers follow: T2 at rank 60 integrates chest, head, and glowing runic overlays. T3 at rank 90 triggers full Spirit Avatar mode — a complete hybrid body transformation representing the peak expression of your martial soul's original form. Each tier is a permanent threshold, not a cooldown."]
