			dependencies: ["6DF58A9163227678"]
			description: ["The Alfheim Portal trades materials from our dimension for rare Elven resources. Throw Livingwood Logs into the active portal to receive Dreamwood in return — the structural timber of Elven Botania builds. To obtain Elementium Ingots, throw Manasteel Ingots through the portal. Each trade has a specific ratio documented in the Lexica Botania. Maintain continuous mana flow to the portal during all trades; if the portal closes mid-trade, the materials are lost. Establish Open Crate automation above the portal for reliable bulk trading."]
