		{
			dependencies: ["18C9A012C3E55667"]
			description: ["Elementium Ingots are obtained by trading Manasteel Ingots through the active Alfheim Portal. They are lighter than Manasteel but resonate more strongly with life energy and fairy affinity — the core material for Botania's endgame armor and the Gaia Spreader. Begin stockpiling immediately: the Gaia Guardian ritual and a full armor set together require a significant quantity, and portal trading is not instantaneous."]
