			dependencies: ["29DAB123D4F66778"]
			description: ["The Gaia Spreader is crafted from Elementium and an Eye of Ender. It transmits mana at twice the speed of a standard Mana Spreader and supports augment Lenses unavailable to its predecessors. Replace your primary mana distribution spreaders once Elementium production is established — the throughput increase sustains larger Botania setups with fewer units and dramatically reduces fill time for the large Mana Pools required by endgame crafting."]
