		{
			dependencies: ["29DAB123D4F66778"]
			description: ["Elementium Armor provides defenses comparable to Terrasteel with a unique Pixie affinity — each piece occasionally summons a Pixie companion when you take damage. Pixies attack your aggressors and draw aggro. A full set significantly increases proc frequency. Apply Epic or Legendary armor stat souls before entering the Gaia Guardian ritual: the fight's escalating damage waves demand sustained mitigation, and the Pixie procs alone will not carry an under-prepared kit."]
