		{
			dependencies: ["4BFCD345F6B88901"]
			description: ["The Gaia Guardian is Botania's hardest boss — summoned by constructing a ritual platform of Mana Pylons arranged in a ring, then throwing a Runic Catalyst at the center while the pylons are charged with mana. The Runic Catalyst is crafted at the Runic Altar from all four elemental runes combined with Mana Pearl and Mana Diamond. During the fight, the Guardian summons Pixie waves, scales its defense by draining nearby Mana Pools, and targets the arena's pylons. Carry a charged Mana Tablet for emergency mana sustain. Defeat it to claim Gaia Ingots — Botania's endgame currency."]
