		{
			dependencies: [
				"09A01ED1974A1836"
				"38C29C6628EE73D9"
			]
			description: ["The Reinforced Slate is created by infusing a Blank Slate with 5,000 LP at the Blood Altar — your first Tier 2 crafting operation. With Reinforced Slates in hand, the altar can be upgraded to Tier 2, granting access to the Apprentice Blood Orb and mid-tier recipes. Build at least four before proceeding; the upgrade path ahead demands them in multiples. The Blood Coagulation Herb significantly offsets the health cost of large LP expenditures — keep a supply on hand during heavy sacrifice sessions."]
