		{
			dependencies: ["6D1EF567B8DAA123"]
			description: ["The Apprentice Blood Orb stores 10,000 LP — five times the capacity of the Weak Blood Orb. Its construction requires a Reinforced Slate and 10,000 LP consumed at the T2 altar. Equipping it in your off-hand makes stored LP available for sigil casting in the field, removing your dependency on returning to the altar for every expenditure. With the Apprentice Orb active, Tier 2 sigils become craftable — each providing a different passive or active LP utility unavailable through any other system in the pack."]
