		{
			dependencies: ["7E2FA678C9EBB234"]
			description: ["The Master Ritual Stone is the anchor for Blood Magic's ritual system — permanent multiblock structures that perform passive LP operations at scale. Each ritual consists of a Master Ritual Stone surrounded by rings of Ritual Stones in a unique elemental pattern. The Well of Suffering, your most important early ritual, places hostile mobs near the altar and sacrifices them continuously to feed your LP reserves — eliminating the need for repeated self-sacrifice at scale."]
