		}
		{
			dependencies: ["1D473E5008CA161A"]
			description: ["The Well of Suffering ritual requires a Master Ritual Stone at center with rings of Ritual Stones in the correct pattern. Once active, it damages all living entities within its radius and converts their health loss directly into LP in the altar. Place a mob spawner above the ritual inside a contained room — a constant sacrificial supply means your altar is always filled and never bottlenecked by your own health pool. This ritual is the backbone of automated LP generation for the rest of your Blood Magic progression."]
